{"name": "17 - Conditions", "_id": "7470a07f7581c21e", "pages": [{"sort": 1, "name": "Conditions", "type": "text", "_id": "a17e6511e5f37cb0", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 0}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": ""}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.a17e6511e5f37cb0"}, {"sort": 2, "name": "Condition Immunity", "type": "text", "_id": "1c4f8b74912735d6", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 2}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>When you have Immunity to a Condition, you completely ignore its effects.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.1c4f8b74912735d6"}, {"sort": 3, "name": "Conditions List", "type": "text", "_id": "ad7078cbc9a426fd", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 2}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": ""}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.ad7078cbc9a426fd"}, {"sort": 4, "name": "Bleeding", "type": "text", "_id": "2f734fbaa3b8881f", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You take <strong>1 </strong>True damage at the start of each of your turns.</p><p><strong>Ending Bleeding</strong> <strong><em>Healed: </em></strong>You\u2019re subjected to an effect that restores your HP.</p><p><strong><em>Medicine Action: </em></strong>A creature can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to make a <strong>DC 10 </strong> Medicine Check on itself or another creature within 1 Space.<strong> </strong> <strong>Success:</strong> Removes the Bleeding Condition. <strong>Success (each 5): </strong> The creature gains +1 Temp HP.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.2f734fbaa3b8881f"}, {"sort": 5, "name": "Blinded", "type": "text", "_id": "f077694c532c91db", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You automatically fail Checks that require Sight and all other creatures are considered <strong>Unseen</strong>. You are <strong>Exposed </strong>(Attacks against you have ADV) and <strong>Hindered </strong>(You have DisADV on Attacks). Additionally, while you\u2019re not guided by another creature, all terrain is Difficult Terrain to you (moving 1 Space costs 2 Spaces).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.f077694c532c91db"}, {"sort": 6, "name": "Burning", "type": "text", "_id": "1e9464c8b54021be", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You take <strong>1</strong> Fire damage at the start of each of your turns. You or another creature within 1 Space can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to put it out.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.1e9464c8b54021be"}, {"sort": 7, "name": "Charmed", "type": "text", "_id": "259439ab9009626a", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>Your Charmer has ADV on Charisma Checks made against you. Additionally, you can\u2019t target your Charmer with harmful Attacks, abilities, or magic effects.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.259439ab9009626a"}, {"sort": 8, "name": "Dazed", "type": "text", "_id": "a5374646c90ea762", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You have DisADV on Mental Checks.</p><p><strong><em>Heavily Dazed: </em></strong>You also have DisADV on Mental Saves.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.a5374646c90ea762"}, {"sort": 9, "name": "Deafened", "type": "text", "_id": "7a13ed2c7b473092", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You automatically fail Checks that require Hearing, and all creatures are considered Unheard by you. Additionally, you have <strong>Resistance </strong>to Sonic damage.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.7a13ed2c7b473092"}, {"sort": 10, "name": "Doomed X", "type": "text", "_id": "640ee4ad46ee9326", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>The HP threshold of Death\u2019s Door for determining death is decreased by an amount equal to the value of X. If your <strong>Doomed </strong>value is ever equal to or higher than your Death's Door threshold, you instantly die upon reaching 0 HP. You lose all stacks of <strong>Doomed </strong>when you complete a Long Rest.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>If your Death\u2019s Door threshold is -3 and you have Doomed 1, the HP threshold of Death\u2019s Door changes from -3 HP to -2 HP, causing you to die if your HP is ever reduced to -2 HP or lower.</div>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.640ee4ad46ee9326"}, {"sort": 11, "name": "Exhaustion X", "type": "text", "_id": "5f854990db081b73", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You gain a penalty equal to X on all Checks and Saves you make. Additionally your Speed and Save DC is reduced by X as well. If a creature ever reaches Exhaustion 6, they immediately die.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>If you have Exhaustion 3, you would have a -3 penalty on Checks and Saves, your Speed would be reduced by 3 Spaces, and your Save DC would be reduced by 3.</div>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.5f854990db081b73"}, {"sort": 12, "name": "Exposed", "type": "text", "_id": "2507619191ed4878", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>Attacks against you have ADV.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.2507619191ed4878"}, {"sort": 13, "name": "Frightened", "type": "text", "_id": "3aa022ab3832a663", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You must spend your turns trying to move as far away as you can from the source of the effect as possible. The only Action you can take is the Move Action to try to run away, or the Dodge Action if you\u2019re prevented from moving or there\u2019s nowhere farther to move. You\u2019re also considered <strong>Rattled </strong>(you can\u2019t move closer to the source) and <strong>Intimidated </strong>(DisADV on all Checks while it\u2019s within your line of sight).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.3aa022ab3832a663"}, {"sort": 14, "name": "Grappled", "type": "text", "_id": "26e5b30672a2f2ee", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>Your Speed becomes 0 and you have DisADV on Agility Saves.</p><p><strong>Ending a Grapple</strong> <strong><em>Escape Grapple: </em></strong>You can spend <strong>1 AP </strong>to attempt to free yourself from a Grapple. Make a Martial Check contested by the Grappler\u2019s Athletics Check. <strong>Success: </strong>The Grapple immediately ends.</p><p><strong><em>Incapacitated </em></strong> <strong><em>Grappler: </em></strong> If the Grappler becomes</p><p><strong>Incapacitated</strong>, the Grapple immediately ends.</p><p><strong><em>Forced Movement:</em></strong> If an effect attempts to forcibly move you beyond the Grappler\u2019s reach, the Grappler makes the Check or Save instead of you. If the effect targets both you and the Grappler, the Grappler makes 1 Check or Save for both of you. <strong>Success:</strong> The targets of the effect aren\u2019t moved. <strong>Failure:</strong> The Grapple immediately ends, and the targets of the effect are moved.</p><p><strong><em>Falling: </em></strong>If you begin falling while Grappled, and your Grappler isn't falling with you, your Grappler holds you in the air if they can carry your weight.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.26e5b30672a2f2ee"}, {"sort": 15, "name": "Hindered", "type": "text", "_id": "d364b24318878371", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You have DisADV on Attacks.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.d364b24318878371"}, {"sort": 16, "name": "Impaired", "type": "text", "_id": "4dd13dd1f69eb979", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You have DisADV on Physical Checks.</p><p><strong><em>Heavily Impaired:</em></strong> You also have DisADV on Physical Saves.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.4dd13dd1f69eb979"}, {"sort": 17, "name": "Incapacitated", "type": "text", "_id": "28741dbfb0f76b1f", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You can\u2019t Speak, Concentrate, or spend Action Points.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.28741dbfb0f76b1f"}, {"sort": 18, "name": "Intimidated", "type": "text", "_id": "b84fea814870008c", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You have DisADV on all Checks while your source of intimidation is within your line of sight.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.b84fea814870008c"}, {"sort": 19, "name": "Invisible", "type": "text", "_id": "03d421bed31a57c0", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You\u2019re <strong>Unseen</strong>, making creatures that can\u2019t see you <strong>Exposed </strong> (your Attacks against them have ADV) and <strong>Hindered </strong>against you (they have DisADV on Attacks against you).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.03d421bed31a57c0"}, {"sort": 20, "name": "Paralyzed", "type": "text", "_id": "f11c3bbb85280844", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>Attacks made from within 1 Space that hit you are considered Critical Hits. You\u2019re also <strong>Stunned </strong>(automatically fail Agility, Might, and Physical Saves), <strong>Exposed </strong>(Attacks against you have ADV), and <strong>Incapacitated </strong>(you can\u2019t Speak, Concentrate, or spend Action Points).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.f11c3bbb85280844"}, {"sort": 21, "name": "Petrified", "type": "text", "_id": "841bd7172a6c65ac", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You and your mundane belongings are turned into stone and you\u2019re no longer aware of your surroundings. You become 10 times heavier and have <strong>Resistance (Half) </strong>to all damage. Any Poisons or Diseases already affecting you are suspended and you\u2019re immune to any additional Poison and Disease while Petrified.</p><p>You\u2019re also <strong>Paralyzed </strong>(Attacks that Hit you are considered Critical Hits if the Attacker is within 1 Space of you), <strong>Stunned </strong> (automatically fail Agility, Might, and Physical Saves), <strong>Exposed </strong>(Attacks against you have ADV), and <strong>Incapacitated </strong> (you can\u2019t Speak, Concentrate, or spend Action Points).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.841bd7172a6c65ac"}, {"sort": 22, "name": "Poisoned", "type": "text", "_id": "d4f7d331064600ea", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You\u2019re <strong>Impaired</strong> (DisADV on Physical Checks) and take <strong>1 </strong> Poison damage at the start of each of your turns. A creature can spend<strong> 1 AP</strong> to make a Medicine Check (against the DC of the Poison) on itself or another creature within 1 Space. <strong>Success: </strong>Removes the Poisoned Condition.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.d4f7d331064600ea"}, {"sort": 23, "name": "Prone", "type": "text", "_id": "78d57fafb2f0d47e", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>While <strong>Prone</strong>, you\u2019re subjected to the following effects:</p><ul><li>You\u2019re<strong>Hindered</strong>(You have DisADV on Attacks).</li><li>Ranged Attacks are<strong>Hindered</strong>against you.</li><li>You\u2019re<strong>Exposed</strong>(Attacks against you have ADV) against Melee Attacks.</li></ul><p><strong><em>Crawling: </em></strong>Your only movement option is to Crawl, which counts as Slowed 1 (Every 1 Space you move costs an extra 1 Space of movement).</p><p><strong><em>Standing Up: </em></strong>You can spend 2 Spaces of movement to stand up, ending the <strong>Prone </strong>Condition on yourself. Standing up from Prone provokes Opportunity Attacks.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.78d57fafb2f0d47e"}, {"sort": 24, "name": "Rattled", "type": "text", "_id": "a9ebed1a2229a23d", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You can\u2019t willingly move closer to your source of fear, and you\u2019re <strong>Intimidated </strong>(DisADV on all Checks while it\u2019s within your line of sight).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.a9ebed1a2229a23d"}, {"sort": 25, "name": "Restrained", "type": "text", "_id": "34d6841b069fe825", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You\u2019re <strong>Hindered</strong> (you have DisADV on Attacks), <strong>Exposed </strong> (Attacks against you have ADV), and <strong>Grappled </strong>(your Speed is reduced to 0 and you have DisADV on Agility Saves).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.34d6841b069fe825"}, {"sort": 26, "name": "Slowed", "type": "text", "_id": "12baa5af70fd911e", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>Every 1 Space you move costs an extra 1 Space of movement.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.12baa5af70fd911e"}, {"sort": 27, "name": "Stunned", "type": "text", "_id": "8d78ef1f2667dc23", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You automatically fail Agility, Might, and Physical Saves. You\u2019re also <strong>Exposed </strong>(Attacks against you have ADV) and <strong>Incapacitated </strong>(you can\u2019t Speak, Concentrate, or spend Action Points).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.8d78ef1f2667dc23"}, {"sort": 28, "name": "Surprised", "type": "text", "_id": "047226f17d2dc62f", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You can\u2019t spend Action Points and are <strong>Exposed </strong>(Attacks against you have ADV).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.047226f17d2dc62f"}, {"sort": 29, "name": "Taunted", "type": "text", "_id": "be22f2dd54351826", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You have DisADV on Attacks against creatures other than the one that Taunted you.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.be22f2dd54351826"}, {"sort": 30, "name": "Unconscious", "type": "text", "_id": "8e821a260a6219f1", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>You\u2019re no longer aware of your surroundings, you drop whatever you\u2019re holding, and you fall <strong>Prone</strong>.</p><p>You\u2019re also <strong>Paralyzed </strong>(Attacks made from within 1 Space that Hit you are considered Critical Hits), <strong>Stunned </strong>(automatically fail Agility, Might, and Physical Saves), <strong>Exposed </strong>(Attacks against you have ADV), and <strong>Incapacitated </strong>(you can\u2019t Speak, Concentrate, or spend Action Points).</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.8e821a260a6219f1"}, {"sort": 31, "name": "Condition Stacking", "type": "text", "_id": "df23e78605e37f6a", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 2}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>Certain Conditions can stack multiple times, increasing the potency of the Condition\u2019s effects on the target.</p>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.df23e78605e37f6a"}, {"sort": 32, "name": "Condition X Values", "type": "text", "_id": "f07eb4afcf3541b2", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>The Conditions with an X value in its name are examples of Conditions that apply a bonus or penalty to the target equal to the X value. If multiple unique effects impose the same Condition X, the X of those effects are added together.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>For the Exhausted X Condition, if you had Exhausted 2, you\u2019d subtract 2 from all d20 rolls made. If you had Exhausted 3, you\u2019d subtract 3, and so on.</div>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.f07eb4afcf3541b2"}, {"sort": 33, "name": "Stacking Conditions", "type": "text", "_id": "ad174deffd2d1c89", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<p>A target can be affected by each of the following Conditions multiple times, with the effects of the same Condition stacking on the target in unique ways.</p><p><strong><em>Durations:</em></strong> When a creature is subjected to the same Condition multiple times but with different durations, it\u2019s important to keep track of the source of each Condition so you know when each Condition ends.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>You might be Exposed against the next Attack against you, Exposed until the end of your next turn, and Exposed for 1 minute, all at the same time. These effects stack, but you need to track them independently to make sure you know how \u201cExposed\u201d you currently are.</div><p><strong>Exposed</strong> A creature can be <strong>Exposed </strong>multiple times. They have stacking ADV equal to the number of sources of <strong>Exposed </strong>it\u2019s subjected to.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>If you were Exposed and another effect imposed the Condition on you again, you would become Exposed twice (Exposed 2), causing Attacks against you to have ADV 2 (roll 3 d20s and take the highest).</div><p><strong>Hindered, Impaired, & Dazed</strong> A creature can be <strong>Hindered</strong>, <strong>Impaired</strong>, or <strong>Dazed </strong>multiple times. They have stacking DisADV equal to the number of sources of each Condition it\u2019s subjected to.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>If you are Restrained (which causes you to be Hindered), and then fall Prone (also causing you to be Hindered), you now would have 2 stacks of Hindered (Hindered 2) and roll at DisADV 2 on all Attacks.</div><p><strong>Slowed</strong> A creature can be <strong>Slowed </strong>multiple times. They have a stacking penalty to their Speed equal to the number of sources of <strong>Slowed </strong>it\u2019s subjected to.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>A creature with Slowed must spend 2 Spaces (1 +1 extra) of movement to move every 1 Space. Alternatively, a creature with two stacks of Slowed (Slowed 2) requires spending 3 Spaces (1 +2 extra) to move 1 Space.</div>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.ad174deffd2d1c89"}, {"sort": 34, "name": "Overlapping Conditions", "type": "text", "_id": "acd8fa8f1f73d14b", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": "<div class=\"book-block book-block-dctip>A good example of being surrounded would be a creature flanked on 4 sides. The GM determines if a creature is surrounded or not.</div><p><strong>Restrained</strong> A creature that\u2019s <strong>Restrained </strong>by more than 1 creature only suffers the effects of the <strong>Restrained </strong>Condition once. However, a creature <strong>Restrained </strong>by multiple sources will remain <strong>Restrained </strong>until they are free from being <strong>Restrained </strong> by all sources.</p><p><strong>Taunted</strong> A creature can only be <strong>Taunted </strong>by 1 creature at a time. If they\u2019re <strong>Taunted </strong>again by another creature, the first Taunt immediately ends.</p><div class=\"book-block book-block-example>If a Goblin is Taunted by a Ranger, then later becomes Taunted by a Fighter, the Goblin is no longer Taunted by the Ranger.</div>"}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.acd8fa8f1f73d14b"}, {"sort": 35, "name": "Non-Stacking Conditions", "type": "text", "_id": "e02b73db547cfb92", "system": {}, "title": {"show": true, "level": 3}, "image": {}, "text": {"format": 1, "content": ""}, "video": {"controls": true, "volume": 0.5}, "src": null, "ownership": {"default": -1, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal.pages!7470a07f7581c21e.e02b73db547cfb92"}], "folder": null, "sort": 0, "ownership": {"default": 0, "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y": 3}, "flags": {}, "_stats": {"compodiumSource": null, "duplicateSource": null, "coreVersion": "12.327", "systemId": "dc20rpg", "systemVersion": "0.8.0", "createdTime": 1721332009.299054, "modifiedTime": 1721332009.299054, "lastModifiedBy": "dOcXwrUs2VunZl0y"}, "_key": "!journal!7470a07f7581c21e"}